                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/5506" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-0834</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">7997 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">国泰租赁ABS债发行的“天时地利人和”</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Guotai Leasing Limited .Company Issuing ABS Bonds at the right time, the right place and the right people</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">胡志颖，姚金欢</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北京科技大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">国泰租赁有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">贸易与金融业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">23 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">ABS债；资产证券化；交易结构；基础资产</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">ABS bonds   Asset Securitization   Transaction structure   Basic assets</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020年以来，宏观经济下行压力较大，融资租赁行业遭遇了由于外部环境变化所导致的行业整体规模回落困境。尤其在近几年“去杠杆”背景下，非金融租赁企业筹资成本较高，资金规模受限。由于融资租赁业务大多是中长期项目，其业务现金流期限与债务期限不匹配，经常面临资金紧张的问题。因此，部分企业开始尝试资产证券化等途径降低流动性风险。国泰租赁有限公司就是其中一家，2021年1月国泰租赁成功发行企业债权类ABS——国泰租赁1期资产支持专项计划，占尽了“天时地利人和”。本案例讨论了发行ABS债的原因、基础资产、交易结构、产品分层设计等诸多问题，为学生充分理解融资工具的选择与运用，ABS债发行过程，金融产品创新等理论提供了丰富的教学素材。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Since 2020, the macro-economy has been under great downward pressure, and the financial leasing industry has encountered the dilemma of the overall scale decline caused by the changes of external environment. Especially in the context of &quot;deleveraging&quot; in recent years, the financing cost of non-financial leasing enterprises is high, and the scale of capital is limited. Because most of the financial leasing business is medium and long-term projects, the short-term loans do not match the term of the leasing business, often facing the problem of capital shortage. Therefore, some enterprises began to try to reduce the liquidity risk by means of asset securitization. Guotai Leasing Limited .Company is one of them. In January 2021, Guotai Leasing Co. Ltd. successfully issued ABS, a special asset support plan for Guotai Leasing (phase 1), which is a kind of enterprise creditor&#39;s rights , and has occupied &quot;favorable time, favorable location and harmonious people&quot;. This case discusses the reasons for issuing ABS bonds, basic assets, transaction structure, product hierarchical design and many other issues. It provides rich teaching materials for students to fully understand the selection and application of financing tools, ABS bond issuance process, financial product innovation and other theories.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《公司理财》、《金融信托与租赁》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">融资方案、金融工具、ABS</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021-09</td>
                            </tr>
